50 - Monster Summoning II<br>
51 - Vocerate: Earth<br>
52 - Vocerate: Fire<br>
53 - Vocerate: Air<br>
54 - Vocerate: Water<br>
55 - Rage of Zomm<br>
56 - Dyzil's Deafening Decoy<br>
57 - Greater Voceration: Earth (Upgraded)<br>
58 - Greater Voceration: Fire (Upgraded to cast new spells)<br>
59 - Greater Voceration: Air (Upgraded)<br>
60 - Greater Voceration: Water (Upgraded)<br>
60 - Monster Summoning III<br>
<br>
Currently &quot;useless&quot; pets:<br>
1. Monster Summoning (needs some edge to make it worthwhile casting, other than the 'illusion'.)<br>
2. Rage of Zomm.  Single Target pet with less than 100 HP, like Cleric Hammer and Wizard Sword, used to be situational a long time ago as it weilds a 2HS and hits for high damage, now pathetic compared to recent pet upgrades.<br>
3.  Dyzil's Deafening Decoy.  Nice taunt, no melee or HP upgrades makes it virtually useless. <p><FONT SIZE="3" COLOR=#FFFFFF FACE="Comic Sans MS, Sans-Serif, Courier New, Verdana, Arial, Helvetica">
